      "type": "text",
      "headline": "IPTV Player for MSX",
      "text": "Version: 1.0.0\n\nA feature-rich IPTV player for Media Station X.\n\nFeatures:\n• M3U/M3U8 playlist support\n• IP server support (Xtream Codes)\n• Subtitle support (multi-language)\n• Live TV streaming\n• Channel categories\n• Favorites management\n• Search functionality\n• EPG support (if provided)\n• HLS & MPEG-TS streaming\n\nSupported Formats:\n• M3U playlists (local & remote)\n• Xtream Codes API servers\n• HTTP/HTTPS streams\n• HLS (m3u8) streams\n• MPEG-TS streams\n• SRT/VTT subtitles\n\nHow to Use:\n1. Add content sources:\n   - 'Playlists' → 'Add M3U Playlist'\n   - 'Playlists' → 'Add IP Server'\n2. Configure subtitles (optional):\n   - 'Subtitles' → 'Add Subtitle Server'\n3. Browse channels in 'Live TV'\n4. Click a channel to start watching\n5. Search for subtitles in your language\n\nFor best experience, use playlists with valid stream URLs.\n\nDeveloped for Media Station X\nhttps://msx.benzac.de"
